generate_service "flat-tire-change" "Flat Tire Change Service" "Got a flat tire in Queens? Our mobile tire change service comes to you." "A flat tire can happen at any time — hitting a pothole on Queens Boulevard, running over debris on the BQE, or discovering a flat in your driveway. Our flat tire change service sends a trained technician to your location in Queens to swap your flat for your spare tire quickly and safely. If you do not have a spare, we can tow your vehicle to the nearest tire shop." "Our service vehicles carry professional-grade jacks, lug wrenches, and tire-changing equipment suitable for all vehicle types from compact cars to large SUVs. We handle standard spare tire installations, donut spare setups, and can even re-inflate tires with minor punctures using portable compressors." '<li><strong>Flat tire on the highway</strong> — Dangerous situation requiring immediate roadside help</li><li><strong>Flat tire in a parking lot</strong> — Cannot drive to a shop</li><li><strong>Multiple flat tires</strong> — Pothole damage on Queens streets</li><li><strong>No spare tire available</strong> — We can tow to nearest tire shop</li><li><strong>Lug nuts stuck or stripped</strong> — Professional tools needed</li>'

